


Step 1: Download SUMO source code from here: https://github.com/eclipse/sumo

Step 2: To add new car following model, go to this website and follow the steps
https://sumo.dlr.de/docs/Developer/How_To/Car-Following_Model.html

Step 3: Build the source code after modification(Adding new car following model) by following the link
https://sumo.dlr.de/docs/Installing/Windows_Build.html  [For Windows]
https://sumo.dlr.de/docs/Installing/Linux_Build.html [For Linux, Ubuntu]

Step 4: Once Compiled, then you can run SUMO from bin folder (Which contains new car following model)

